- Infrastructure segmentation in the MVNO Market includes Skinny MVNOs, Thin MVNOs, and Thick MVNOs. This categorization helps MVNOs optimize their network infrastructure and service offerings based on the level of control and ownership they desire.

- Operational Model segmentation in the MVNO Market encompasses Reseller MVNOs, Service Operator MVNOs, and Full MVNOs. This segmentation helps MVNOs define their business operations, partnerships, and service strategies to meet the needs of their target market segments effectively.

